# Jerk Rice and Peas Bowl

Based on [https://www.africanbites.com/one-pot-caribbean-jerk-chicken-rice/](https://www.africanbites.com/one-pot-caribbean-jerk-chicken-rice/) and [https://www.thekitchn.com/jerk-chicken-jamaican-rice-and-peas-recipe-256069](https://www.thekitchn.com/jerk-chicken-jamaican-rice-and-peas-recipe-256069)

